<item>
            <title>[JCR-707] Range queries fail on large repositories</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCR-707</link>
                <project id="10591" key="JCR">Jackrabbit Content Repository</project>
                        <description>As discussed on the user mailing list, queries on large repositories with date constraints like &amp;quot;field &amp;gt; constant&amp;quot; treat the constraint as always true, returning results that should not be returned.</description>
